{"tid":1573653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制TVB : wewa卡挑戰再升級","createTime":"2019-09-16T05:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T00:49:24.000Z","uid":113630,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"35d743bc568dda54a65c8aa2fa8eb04974c964ed","tid":1573653,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"如果唔知上個post發生咩事嘅話就喺度睇返<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>新一波玩死TVB行動 - wewa卡挑戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1564956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1564956</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">TVB 第二大廣告收入係：財務公司</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n要斷TVB米路，抵制廣告商是常識，而TVB第二大廣告客戶類別就係貸款及按揭公司，當然要爭取佢哋撤回廣告。不過財務公司好難抵制，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其中一個大客就係安信</strong></span></span>，呢排係咁喺TVB<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">賣wewa卡廣告</span></strong></span>，佢哋成日sell大學生申請，所以可能好多後生仔都有一張，有咭嘅連登仔一定可以參與。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 剪卡</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>已經有幾位手足響應剪卡</strong></span>，但係可惜FB玩嘢，幾張剪卡相都睇唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRncWsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRncWsu.jpg&h=9822bfc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2eKnzea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2eKnzea.jpg&h=a45782d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2. Up 上FB</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家剪卡後除咗擺張剪卡相上wewa FB外 (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WeWaMode/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWeWaMode%2F&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=2d5315ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WeWaMode/</a>)，<br />\nTemplate：無綫新聞，誤導市民！安信落TVB廣告？不了<br />\n<br />\n仲要擺喺自己status度 hashtag #wewachallenge，再tag @WeWa玩嘢mode，標題寫&ldquo;安信兄弟資助TVB假新聞，恥與為伍&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 大學貼Poster</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n更加重要嘅係，由於呢張卡係主要sell大學生申請，所以麻煩各位幫手將呢幅宣傳海報貼喺各大專院校嘅連儂牆、民主牆或其他貼得嘅地方度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmdfM7J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmdfM7J.png&h=2cc6286d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>PDF 高清File:</strong></span> <a href=\"https://gofile.io/?c=6qNqJy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgofile.io%2F%3Fc%3D6qNqJy&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=4f43c3e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gofile.io/?c=6qNqJy</a><br />\n<br />\n最好連埋呢張圖擺上去，加強效果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTqYR0D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTqYR0D.jpg&h=16e87cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂各位！"},{"pid":"d97161a991f0dc19973ee79683e06a97bcd88b40","tid":1573653,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ac4c420e7a47c2f732dbc156cf65c7f5092d8e","tid":1573653,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"740ad1952c5afed6fea97bc0ca2f150fe3f4a5fb","tid":1573653,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1397bcf250eeb36f928fc053e225af8eb4f4a2fb","tid":1573653,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:27:07.000Z","msg":"撞"},{"pid":"e737846a09015133449630628fa6e4864f537611","tid":1573653,"uid":266747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n手足搵命博，齊做文宣公關；再落力d<br />\n@組隊兜路以防跟蹤狂魔<br />\n@期望連仔幫手壓制fake news <br />\n@上連登要用多用腦！<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆戰線受襲！唱歌後連儂，有你有我<br />\n考驗毅力與堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做更具價值嘅野<br />\n#離開同溫層，接觸各種人，理解佢地嘅想法，將不支持我們的人轉為支持我們！這是成功的方法！<br />\n<br />\n@Template@<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 優先幫襯良心商店<br />\n2. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶<br />\n3. 抵制港鐵（注意安全）；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚十點咆哮！（改9點會少好多人）<br />\n5. 健身+運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. 每日一post，國際戰線（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=424eb6e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，冷處理fake news/ rumour 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 低消費，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，教育家中兩老<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF轉美國<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.16 @Template End@"},{"pid":"1999a1896613965a2d465cdd817fe67a4d438373","tid":1573653,"uid":106278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"你search下安信係咩背景就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43be21a944633cee55fa034eb90ac8ae34eff236","tid":1573653,"uid":262379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc7e664dcae5c5056a7a91addf137ecc1ba9af76","tid":1573653,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"gd"},{"pid":"1c70a31b7a2c713ee51da13330c6e6f501469f99","tid":1573653,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986be3df7674d5a48e1fb73eb5137a2fdf668173","tid":1573653,"uid":71382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0a5ca7f23ecba629e8ff87141a0e559f53c051","tid":1573653,"uid":73163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"黃&amp;藍餐廳list <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restart-hk.com%2FShopList.html&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=9d732e05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html</a>"},{"pid":"f1d70f8b4e003c5530062617527c996e8165fed7","tid":1573653,"uid":59737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"TVB 死仆街"},{"pid":"736fec2af018fae36aa80d1